### 1) Create supplier
POST http://localhost:5258/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "email": "supplier@acme.test",
  "currency": "USD",
  "country": "US"
}

### 2) Create category
POST http://localhost:5258/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "shortcode": "ELEC"
}

### 3) List suppliers
GET http://localhost:5258/suppliers

### 4) List categories
GET http://localhost:5258/categories

### 5) Create product (replace IDs)
POST http://localhost:5258/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierId": "REPLACE_SUPPLIER_ID",
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_CATEGORY_ID",
  "description": "Gaming Laptop",
  "acquisitionCostSupplierCurrency": 1200.00,
  "acquisitionCostUSD": 1200.00,
  "acquireDate": "2025-08-12T03:00:00Z"
}

### 6) List products
GET http://localhost:5258/products

### 7) Get product by id
GET http://localhost:5258/products/REPLACE_PRODUCT_ID

### 8) Mark Sold
POST http://localhost:5258/products/REPLACE_PRODUCT_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": 1,
  "timestamp": "2025-08-12T04:00:00Z"
}

### 9) Try invalid transition (Cancelled -> Sold should 400)
POST http://localhost:5258/products/REPLACE_PRODUCT_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": 2,
  "timestamp": "2025-08-12T05:00:00Z"
}

### 10) Now attempt Sold again (should 400 if already Cancelled/Returned)
POST http://localhost:5258/products/REPLACE_PRODUCT_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": 1,
  "timestamp": "2025-08-12T05:30:00Z"
}
